Package: evbt
Architecture: all
Depends: openjdk-25-jre-headless, ${misc:Depends}
Description: EventBTool - code generation and documentation for Event-B
 EventBTool (evbt) produces source code and documentation from Event-B models.
 It is a command-line application distributed as a self-contained Java archive.
 .
 The jar targets a recent Java release; this package pulls in a suitable
 headless JRE and provides the "evbt" launcher.
